Interface HasObjectHelper

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    SymbolMap, SymbolMap.Fluid, SymbolMap.Solid
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DagClass, DownNodeClass, EntityMixin, GraphClass, IdDagClass, IdGraphClass, IdTreeClass, ObjectMixin, TreeClass, UpNodeClass, ValueMixin

    public interface HasObjectHelper
    An object with an ObjectHelper, which will usually be in instance of ValueMixin or EntityMixin.
